Welcome to Project Arctic circle theorem 's documentation!
==========================================================

.. image:: data:image/png;base64,
   :alt: arctic circle
   :align: center

Arctic Circle Theroem is a package allowing the vizualisation of two elements :

   1) Random paving of dominoes 

   2) An observation of the arctic circle phenomenon 

  
Hope you can find in this package something to satisfy your curiosity !
